name: Time
description: It started with a message when technology was getting faster and more powerful, but behind that there are still people who isolate themselves from technology. Actually what they really need is the introduction and use of technology as a tool instead of being afraid of it, technology is here to help human do things easily and create new things that human can't do. it would be nice if we were united with the "chaos" of technology, which previously did not get along with technology, now we can get along with technology and make good friends because we can merge with technology into one, no longer as something foreign to us.
